<devicesets>
<deviceset name="WE-TVS-HS_SOT23-6L_82400102" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:14282999/5" prefix="D" library_version="6">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-TVS TVS Diode – High Speed Series
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Characteristics
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Low clamping voltage
&lt;br&gt;Sturdy design
&lt;br&gt;Very low capacitance
&lt;br&gt;Flow Thru Design for a simple layout
&lt;br&gt;Rail to Rail protection
&lt;br&gt;Epoxy flame resistant UL94-V0
&lt;br&gt;RoHS, REACH and free of halogens

&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Very fast data lines
&lt;br&gt;USB 2.0
&lt;br&gt;Ethernet
&lt;br&gt;PoE
&lt;br&gt;VGA
&lt;br&gt;Sim Cards
&lt;br&gt;Keypads
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;B&gt;HS = High Speed
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/media/o14883v209%20Family_WE-TVS_HIGHSPEED.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/media/o14883v209%20Family_WE-TVS_HIGHSPEED.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-HS"&gt;https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-HS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;Updated  by Ella Wu 2021-12-16&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;2021(C) Wurth Elektronik</description>
